                              ውስተ፡ ልብየ፡ እንዘ፡ ትገብር፡ ቀለመ። ደመከ፡ አምላካዊ፡ በመስቀል፡ ዘዘንመ። </q>
                           
                           <note> Written in a fine hand. Cp. WQ-006, UM-008, KAE-001 </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1"><desc>- Title of Text I ገድለ ጭርቆሥ is written in black paint on
                           the outer face of the front board.&#xD; - Titles of some texts in the
                           work are written on <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>.&#xD; - Names written
                           in pen in the upper margin: <locus target="#27r">27r</locus>, 44r.&#xD; -
                           Ethiopic numerals are written in the upper margin (possibly referring to
                           the process of writing and scribal work?): <locus target="#16r">16r</locus>, 23r, 72r.&#xD; - Pen trial: <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>.&#xD; - Corrections written interlineally: e.g., <locus target="#14ra">14ra</locus>, 21rb, 46vb.&#xD; - Words or passages
                           erased: <locus target="#8ra">8ra</locus>, 70ra.&#xD; - Chains of black
                           and red dots as text dividers: <locus target="#86rb">86rb</locus>, 94ra,
                           100vb.</desc></item>
                     </list>
